{"number":11,"verseCount":30,"verses":[[1,[["A",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 29:14","ot/isa/29.14"],"; ",["D&C 4:1 (1–7)","dc-testament/dc/4.1"],"."]]]," great and marvelous work is about to come forth among the children of men."]],[2,["Behold, I am God; give ",["heed",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 1:14 (14, 37)","dc-testament/dc/1.14"],"; ",["84:43 (43–45)","dc-testament/dc/84.43"],"."]]]," to my ",["word",["study-note-ref","b",[["Heb. 4:12","nt/heb/4.12"],"."]]],", which is quick and ",["powerful",["study-note-ref","c",[["Alma 4:19","bofm/alma/4.19"],"; ",["31:5","bofm/alma/31.5"],"."]]],", ",["sharper",["study-note-ref","d",[["Hel. 3:29","bofm/hel/3.29"],"; ",["D&C 6:2","dc-testament/dc/6.2"],"."]]]," than a two-edged sword, to the dividing asunder of both joints and marrow; therefore give ",["heed",["study-note-ref","e",[["1 Ne. 15:25 (23–25)","bofm/1-ne/15.25"],"."]]]," unto my word."]],[3,["Behold, the field is ",["white",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 4:4","dc-testament/dc/4.4"],"."]]]," already to harvest; therefore, whoso desireth to reap let him thrust in his sickle with his ",["might",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Dedication","tg/dedication"],"."]]],", and reap while the day lasts, that he may ",["treasure",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Treasure","tg/treasure"],"."]]]," up for his soul ",["everlasting",["study-note-ref","d",[["1 Tim. 6:19","nt/1-tim/6.19"],"."]]]," salvation in the kingdom of God."]],[4,["Yea, whosoever will thrust in his sickle and ",["reap",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Harvest","tg/harvest"],"."]]],", the same is ",["called",["study-note-ref","b",[["Rev. 14:15","nt/rev/14.15"],"; ",["D&C 4:3","dc-testament/dc/4.3"],"; ",["6:4","dc-testament/dc/6.4"],"; ",["12:4 (3–4)","dc-testament/dc/12.4"],"; ",["14:4 (3–4)","dc-testament/dc/14.4"],"."]]]," of God."]],[5,["Therefore, if you will ask of me you shall receive; if you will ",["knock",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Objectives","tg/objectives"],"; ",["Prayer","tg/prayer"],"."]]]," it shall be opened unto you."]],[6,["Now, as you have asked, behold, I say unto you, keep my commandments, and seek to bring forth and establish the cause of ",["Zion",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 52:8","ot/isa/52.8"],"; ",["D&C 66:11","dc-testament/dc/66.11"],". ",["TG Zion","tg/zion"],"."]]],"."]],[7,["Seek not for ",["riches",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Kgs. 3:11 (11–13)","ot/1-kgs/3.11"],"; ",["2 Ne. 26:31","bofm/2-ne/26.31"],"; ",["Jacob 2:18 (17–19)","bofm/jacob/2.18"],"; ",["D&C 38:39","dc-testament/dc/38.39"],"."]]]," but for ",["wisdom",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Education","tg/education"],"; ",["Wisdom","tg/wisdom"],"."]]],"; and, behold, the mysteries of God shall be unfolded unto you, and then shall you be made ",["rich",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Treasure","tg/treasure"],"."]]],". Behold, he that hath eternal life is rich."]],[8,["Verily, verily, I say unto you, even as you desire of me so it shall be done unto you; and, if you desire, you shall be the means of doing much good in this generation."]],[9,[["Say",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 19:21 (21–22)","dc-testament/dc/19.21"],"."]]]," nothing but ",["repentance",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Repent","tg/repent"],"."]]]," unto this generation. Keep my commandments, and assist to bring forth my ",["work",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG God, Works of","tg/god-works-of"],"."]]],", ",["according",["study-note-ref","d",[["D&C 105:5","dc-testament/dc/105.5"],"."]]]," to my commandments, and you shall be blessed."]],[10,["Behold, thou hast a ",["gift",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 46:8","dc-testament/dc/46.8"],"."]]],", or thou shalt have a gift if thou wilt desire of me in faith, with an ",["honest",["study-note-ref","b",[["Luke 8:15","nt/luke/8.15"],". ",["TG Motivations","tg/motivations"],"."]]]," heart, believing in the power of Jesus Christ, or in my power which speaketh unto thee;"]],[11,["For, behold, it is I that speak; behold, I am the ",["light",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Light of Christ","tg/light-of-christ"],"."]]]," which shineth in darkness, and by my ",["power",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Authority of","tg/jesus-christ-authority-of"],"."]]]," I give these words unto thee."]],[12,["And now, verily, verily, I say unto thee, put your ",["trust",["study-note-ref","a",[["Prov. 28:25 (25–26)","ot/prov/28.25"],"; ",["D&C 84:116","dc-testament/dc/84.116"],". ",["TG Trust in God","tg/trust-in-god"],"."]]]," in that ",["Spirit",["study-note-ref","b",[["Rom. 8:1 (1–9)","nt/rom/8.1"],"; ",["1 Jn. 4:1 (1–6)","nt/1-jn/4.1"],". ",["TG God, Spirit of","tg/god-spirit-of"],"."]]]," which ",["leadeth",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Guidance, Divine","tg/guidance-divine"],"."]]]," to do ",["good",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Benevolence","tg/benevolence"],"."]]],"—yea, to do ",["justly",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Justice","tg/justice"],"."]]],", to walk ",["humbly",["study-note-ref","f",[["TG Humility","tg/humility"],"."]]],", to ",["judge",["study-note-ref","g",[["Matt. 7:1 (1–5)","nt/matt/7.1"],"; ",["Rom. 14:4 (4–6)","nt/rom/14.4"],"; ",["Alma 41:14 (14–15)","bofm/alma/41.14"],"."]]]," righteously; and this is my Spirit."]],[13,["Verily, verily, I say unto you, I will impart unto you of my Spirit, which shall ",["enlighten",["study-note-ref","a",[["Eph. 1:18","nt/eph/1.18"],"; ",["D&C 76:12","dc-testament/dc/76.12"],". ",["TG Discernment, Spiritual","tg/discernment-spiritual"],"; ",["Inspiration","tg/inspiration"],"; ",["Light of Christ","tg/light-of-christ"],"."]]]," your ",["mind",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Mind","tg/mind"],"."]]],", which shall fill your soul with ",["joy",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Joy","tg/joy"],"."]]],";"]],[14,["And then shall ye know, or by this shall you know, all things whatsoever you desire of me, which are pertaining unto things of ",["righteousness",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Righteousness","tg/righteousness"],"."]]],", in faith believing in me that you shall receive."]],[15,["Behold, I command you that you need not suppose that you are ",["called",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Authority","tg/authority"],"."]]]," to ",["preach",["study-note-ref","b",[["A of F 1:5","pgp/a-of-f/1.5"],". ",["TG Preaching","tg/preaching"],"."]]]," ",["until",["study-note-ref","c",[["D&C 30:5","dc-testament/dc/30.5"],"."]]]," you are called."]],[16,["Wait a little longer, until you shall have my word, my ",["rock",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 6:34","dc-testament/dc/6.34"],"; ",["10:69","dc-testament/dc/10.69"],"; ",["18:4 (4, 17)","dc-testament/dc/18.4"],"; ",["33:13","dc-testament/dc/33.13"],". ",["TG Rock","tg/rock"],"."]]],", my ",["church",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Church","tg/church"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Head of the Church","tg/jesus-christ-head-of-the-church"],"."]]],", and my gospel, that you may know of a surety my doctrine."]],[17,["And then, behold, according to your desires, yea, even according to your ",["faith",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Faith","tg/faith"],"."]]]," shall it be done unto you."]],[18,["Keep my commandments; hold your peace; appeal unto my Spirit;"]],[19,["Yea, ",["cleave",["study-note-ref","a",[["Josh. 23:8","ot/josh/23.8"],"; ",["Jacob 6:5","bofm/jacob/6.5"],"; ",["Hel. 4:25","bofm/hel/4.25"],"."]]]," unto me with all your heart, that you may assist in bringing to light those things of which has been spoken—yea, the ",["translation",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 10:3","dc-testament/dc/10.3"],"."]]]," of my work; be patient until you shall accomplish it."]],[20,["Behold, this is your work, to ",["keep",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ex. 15:26","ot/ex/15.26"],"; ",["D&C 5:35","dc-testament/dc/5.35"],". ",["TG Commitment","tg/commitment"],"; ",["Obedience","tg/obedience"],"."]]]," my commandments, yea, with all your might, ",["mind",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Dedication","tg/dedication"],"."]]]," and strength."]],[21,["Seek not to ",["declare",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Missionary Work","tg/missionary-work"],"; ",["Preaching","tg/preaching"],"."]]]," my word, but first seek to ",["obtain",["study-note-ref","b",[["Alma 17:2 (2–3)","bofm/alma/17.2"],"; ",["D&C 84:85","dc-testament/dc/84.85"],"."]]]," my ",["word",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Learn","tg/learn"],"; ",["Scriptures, Value of","tg/scriptures-value-of"],"."]]],", and then shall your tongue be loosed; then, if you desire, you shall have my ",["Spirit",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Teaching with the Spirit","tg/teaching-with-the-spirit"],"."]]]," and my word, yea, the power of God unto the ",["convincing",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Conversion","tg/conversion"],"."]]]," of men."]],[22,["But now hold your ",["peace",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ex. 14:14","ot/ex/14.14"],"."]]],"; study ",["my word",["study-note-ref","b",["IE the Bible."]]]," which hath gone forth among the children of men, and also ",["study",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Education","tg/education"],"; ",["Scriptures, Study of","tg/scriptures-study-of"],"; ",["Study","tg/study"],"."]]]," my word which shall come forth among the children of men, or that which is ",["now translating",["study-note-ref","d",["IE the Book of Mormon."]]],", yea, until you have obtained all which I shall ",["grant",["study-note-ref","e",[["Alma 29:8","bofm/alma/29.8"],"; ",["3 Ne. 26:8 (7–10)","bofm/3-ne/26.8"],"."]]]," unto the children of men in this generation, and then shall all things be added thereto."]],[23,["Behold thou art ",["Hyrum",["study-note-ref","a",[["JS—H 1:4","pgp/js-h/1.4"],"."]]],", my son; ",["seek",["study-note-ref","b",[["Matt. 6:33","nt/matt/6.33"],"."]]]," the kingdom of God, and all things shall be added according to that which is just."]],[24,[["Build",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 7:24","nt/matt/7.24"],"."]]]," upon my ",["rock",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Rock","tg/rock"],"."]]],", which is my ",["gospel",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Gospel","tg/gospel"],"."]]],";"]],[25,["Deny not the spirit of ",["revelation",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Revelation","tg/revelation"],"."]]],", nor the spirit of ",["prophecy",["study-note-ref","b",[["Rev. 19:10","nt/rev/19.10"],". ",["TG Prophecy","tg/prophecy"],"."]]],", for wo unto him that ",["denieth",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Apostasy of Individuals","tg/apostasy-of-individuals"],"."]]]," these things;"]],[26,["Therefore, ",["treasure",["study-note-ref","a",[["Deut. 11:18","ot/deut/11.18"],"; ",["D&C 6:20","dc-testament/dc/6.20"],"; ",["43:34","dc-testament/dc/43.34"],"; ",["84:85","dc-testament/dc/84.85"],"; ",["JS—M 1:37","pgp/js-m/1.37"],"."]]]," up in your ",["heart",["study-note-ref","b",[["Prov. 20:5","ot/prov/20.5"],"."]]]," until the time which is in my wisdom that you shall go forth."]],[27,["Behold, I speak unto ",["all",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Mission of Latter-day Saints","tg/mission-of-latter-day-saints"],"."]]]," who have good desires, and have thrust in their sickle to reap."]],[28,["Behold, I am Jesus Christ, the ",["Son of God",["study-note-ref","a",[["Rom. 1:4","nt/rom/1.4"],"."]]],". I am the life and the ",["light",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Light of the World","tg/jesus-christ-light-of-the-world"],"; ",["Light [noun]","tg/light-noun"],"."]]]," of the world."]],[29,["I am the same who came unto mine own and mine own ",["received me not",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Prophets, Rejection of","tg/prophets-rejection-of"],"."]]],";"]],[30,["But verily, verily, I say unto you, that as many as receive me, to them will I give ",["power",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 1:12","nt/john/1.12"],"."]]]," to become the ",["sons",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Sons and Daughters of God","tg/sons-and-daughters-of-god"],"."]]]," of God, even to them that ",["believe",["study-note-ref","c",[["1 Jn. 3:23 (19–24)","nt/1-jn/3.23"],"."]]]," on my name. Amen."]]],"volume":"dc"}